oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: From Folk, to Hillbilly, to Country - What Next? - various interviews - Part 5
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Excerpt from "From Folk, to Hillbilly, to Country - What Next?" thesis for Austin Peay college by Mary Biggs, includes interviews with Doug Green.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Test tones -- Doug Green talks about the origin of some country artists and the country music scene in Austin, TX -- Mary Biggs talks about her thesis project -- Green talks about his career as a musician and other jobs he held -- Biggs talks about working for Murray Nash -- Biggs ends her project
